---
title: Golden Spiced Chicken & Garlic Almond Crumb with Roast Root Veggie Toss & Capsicum Relish
description: Sure, searing up some chicken for dinner is all fine and dandy. But why not take it up a notch with
this aromatic crumb that's scattered over the chicken as a crunchy finishing touch? It'll contrast perfectly with the
capsicum relish. Trust us, this is going to be your new pork dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
